Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:09.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 水野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:16.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了保護你而存在於此的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:18.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:36.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我是來歸還失物的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:49.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\fs28\be1\blur4}第十四話 Eingott之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 總算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在哪裡被撿到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:10.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:14.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子掉了回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你帶我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:20.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:32.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都從這裡跳上車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我總勸她別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這孩子不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:59.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是我很少有機會到女孩子家做客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心跳加速？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特沒去女朋友家玩過？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:08.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 留下來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正奶奶要值夜班也不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水野 可別總讓姐姐操心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一位客人請到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:50.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 這位客人是第一次來我們店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 水野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是想剪頭髮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想剪成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戀愛……吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:14.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:15.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:21.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戀愛 絕對錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛要怎樣才能進展順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:33.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然只有勇往直前啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？和子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然腳本還沒有全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這回有接吻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}(和子妄想中)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是演戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 這回是男女接吻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這可會成為話題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓它變成話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戲劇需要宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:39.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有觀眾的舞台才能被稱作舞台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼演員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意向中的女主角是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:51.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長 和子大人可是皆水之巫女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:57.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓島上神聖的巫女在人前深吻確實不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:04.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂 如果和塔科特演對手戲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我經過慎重考慮後決定申請做候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渴望真是強烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活力四射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕無敵 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再考慮考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謠言四起了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說下一次演出有接吻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備開始了呢 紗理奈部長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼真好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:41.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是塔科特君或者諏訪君的話 我也想申請做候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:44.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是和子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是塔科特君的初吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是接吻也不過是演戲而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來乃如此介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:11.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需多時 Cybody Eingott的再生啟動準備即將就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eingott之眼並非第一階段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若所使用的Cybody本身的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在第二階段以上則是無法使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以為了尋找巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:26.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要求Driver Manticole乘坐電力柩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:31.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以找到還沒出現的巫女麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:16.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是日死之巫女的封印被解開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的Cybody將進化到第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與道伯恩的戰鬥也將向著更有利的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候我才能與Eingott進行Apprivoiser啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是明天也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功與否完全取決於你的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:09:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意 這一刻我等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起歸隊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二場盛會即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了我們Banishing Age的時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱了一個晚上 親吻場景的角色分配現在發表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的親吻場景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定由塔科特君與水野醬這對新生組合出演
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經變成校園內的熱門話題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加了個油 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們加油吧 塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現鞠野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似心情很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢 我第一次的舞台劇演吻戲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了答對了答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一對好姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻戲的女主角不是和子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說……乃……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來看我了麼 真高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作畫時的你看起來真的很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造世界的壓力以及喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪畫的時候 說不定能體會到神的心境呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這真是非常幸福的時光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會的話 我倒很想試著畫一幅你的肖像畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃冰激凌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天想吃什麼味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟鞠野一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天會選擇什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芒果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 每次都對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是看見與我如此相像的你跟塔科特KISS的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會產生一種很奇怪的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果這是你所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一定要守護
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是因此才存在於此的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構成Eingott的oreichalkos開始光子活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了水野 決不能輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野 一定要由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得你一個人啊 塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人無論何時都是獨自生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可聽說了哦 你要在文藝匯演上出演吻戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連您都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子 塔科特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰啊 不戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個Cybody是Eingott嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eingott
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是Eingott
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道他的名字 這是Cybody的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那具Cybody散發著很不詳的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.91,0:24:18.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:20.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有了第三階段近在眼前的實感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eingott之眼 啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請準備出動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以出動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具備能看到巫女所在地之眼的Cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼只有那個Cybody被毀的面目全非呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來要重新思考一下這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四方的……巫女們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野 由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體……動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不許控制我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manticole打算在這兒打倒銀河美少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這不是Manticole
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Eingott自身在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝著這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人的心被控制住了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個邪惡的Cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能讓它復活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Star Sword Emlord
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Star Sword Saphiel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就來救你了 「某人」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪邁銀河十字斬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 我說和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經體驗過KISS了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 秘—密—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在零空間展開的時候 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有日死之巫女了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過Eingott之眼 我確實看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日死之巫女 現在已經不在這個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情已經清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manticole似乎已經察覺你的真實身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 就算把這件事公開了也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎不打算多嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eingott之眼 機能正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\fn微軟雅黑}sāmekh，是王之柱的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「擁有{\fn微軟雅黑}sāmekh{\fn}印記的人在有生之年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的四位巫女必須活著」這個原理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我覺得她在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會像之前一樣 永遠守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼沒事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……塔科特君 果然很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可難辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才能讓她說出來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已經知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她有必要隱瞞的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那個女孩就是日死之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡吃冰激凌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和烏鴉卡斯克是好朋友
